videos.description: South Carolina G Kaela Davis drops 14 points, including going 4-for-4 from deep, as the Gamecocks easily defeat the Saint Peter's Peahens 93-38.
videos.headline: Kaela Davis' 3-point shooting helps South Carolina to victory
